Usage

MainTemporalGroup(alias)

OpenTemporalGroup(
  title = character(0),
  description = character(0),
  contact = character(0),
  rows = integer(0),
  pages = integer(0),
  fields = character(0),
  years = integer(0),
  endpoints = list()
)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

title

<chr> title

description

<chr> description

contact

<chr> contact name and email address

rows

<int> number of rows

pages

<int> number of pages

fields

<chr> field names

years

<int> years available

endpoints

<data.frame> endpoints

Value

An S7 <MainCurrent> object.

An S7 <ProviderCurrent> object.

An S7 <OpenCurrent> object.

An S7 <MainTemporal> object.

An S7 <OpenTemporal> object.

An S7 <MainTemporalGroup> object.

An S7 <TemporalOpenGroup> object.
